text: Charlie Depthios was a weightlifter from Indonesia. Depthios competed at the 1968 Summer Olympics and the 1972 Summer Olympics. He was born on 2 February 1940 and died on 4 September 1999.Charlie Depthios == References == Category:1940 births Category:1999 deaths Category:Indonesian weightlifters Category:Olympians for Indonesia
